      "title": "Rehearsal event in Parliament tomorrow",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The third session of the Ninth Parliament is going to be inaugurated tomorrow (03) by President Ranil Wickremesinghe.",
        "The new president will be accorded a 21-gun salute by security forces at the event, which is being held in compliance with health guidelines."
